TO IMPLEMENT:

Change definition of permission constants to be XML format
and add stuff for menu to these.

{Description}Maintain Add vehicle Window
{Category}Administration
{Internal}False

&lt;Permission&gt;
&lt;Descr&gt;Maintain Add vehicle Window&lt;/Descr&gt;
&lt;Category&gt;Administration&lt;/Category&gt;
&lt;Internal&gt;False&lt;/Internal&gt;
&lt;/Permission&gt;
&lt;MenuDtl&gt;
&lt;Heading&gt;Zzzzz&lt;/Heading&gt;
&lt;ClassToCreate&gt;xxx&lt;/ClassToCreate&gt;
&lt;Schema&gt;yyy&lt;/Schema&gt;
&lt;WinClass&gt;zzz&lt;/WinClass&gt;
&lt;/MenuDtl&gt;</text>
